GNU Wget2 2.0.0 发布于 2021 年 9 月 26 日。<ref name="GNU Wget2 2.0.0">{{Cite web|url=https://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/info-gnu/2021-09/msg00011.html|website=gnu.org|title=GNU Wget2 2.0.0 released|date=2021-09-26|access-date=2021-10-02|archive-date=2022-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220321210919/https://lists.gnu.org/archive/html/info-gnu/2021-09/msg00011.html}}</ref>比起Wget1.x支持以下协议和技术：<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://gitlab.com/gnuwget/wget2|website=GitLab|title=wget2|access-date=2021-10-02|archive-date=2018-03-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180301225435/https://gitlab.com/gnuwget/wget2}}</ref>

* [[HTTP/2|HTTP/2]]
* [[HTTP压缩|HTTP压缩]]
* 并行连接
* 使用[[HTTP头字段|HTTP头字段]]<code>If-Modified-Since</code>
* [[TCP_Fast_Open|TCP Fast Open]]

